[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0432","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0432.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0247","title":"INN nnrpd 缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"INN (InterNetNews) 新闻服务器中的 nnrpd 程序存在栈缓冲区溢出漏洞，版本 1.6 及之前版本受影响。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标系统发送特制的新闻组请求，触发缓冲区溢出，从而在服务器上以 nnrpd 进程权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响广泛部署的 INN 新闻服务器系统，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。建议升级至 INN 1.6 以上版本修复。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0247"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-07-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:59.740","remediation":"升级 INN 至 2.0 或更高版本，该漏洞在 INN 1.7 及后续版本中已被修复。如无法升级，可在 innd 配置中限制 nnrpd 服务的远程访问来源 IP，或禁用 nnrpd 的远程连接功能作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.nai.com/nai_labs/asp_set/advisory/17_inn_avd.asp","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1443","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0247.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0247.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0247","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0247.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0247.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0247.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-69m7-6fwc-hxpx/GHSA-69m7-6fwc-hxpx.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/I/inn.nasl","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0432.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0431","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0431.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0246","title":"HP Remote Watch 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"HP Remote Watch 是 HP-UX 系统上的一款远程监控服务，存在未授权访问漏洞。未经认证的远程攻击者无需任何身份验证即可通过网络直接利用该服务，获取目标系统的完全 root 权限，导致机密性、完整性和可用性完全沦陷。该漏洞 CVSS v2.0 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，攻击复杂度低，影响范围广泛。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0246"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1996-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:59.617","remediation":"立即停止 Remote Watch 服务：执行 `rwatch -k` 终止运行中的守护进程，并从 `/etc/inittab` 或 `/etc/rc.config.d/remotewatch` 中移除自动启动配置。如果业务不需要远程监控功能，彻底卸载 Remote Watch 子系统（`swremove RemoteWatch`）。必须通过防火墙限制 TCP 端口 1770 的入站访问，仅允许受信任的管理 IP 连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0246","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0246.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0246","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0246.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0246.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0246.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-848h-2v7f-436w/GHSA-848h-2v7f-436w.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/R/remwatch.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82085/info.html","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/97009c469920f4d8991128f84d19644c3badca15/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-02xx/CVE-1999-0246.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0431.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0430","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0430.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0245","title":"Linux NIS+ 认证绕过漏洞","description":"Linux NIS+（网络信息服务）在特定配置下存在认证绕过漏洞。当 NIS+ 配置文件中包含\"+\"通配符条目时，系统会将 NIS 映射中的用户信息直接导入本地认证数据库，导致攻击者无需有效凭据即可利用该通配符以任意用户身份登录系统。此漏洞源于 NIS+ 访问控制配置不当，攻击者只需具备本地网络访问权限即可触发，成功利用后可获得受影响系统的未授权访问，进而可能泄露敏感信息或进行后续攻击。该漏洞影响早期 Linux 发行版中启用 NIS+ 服务且未正确限制通配符条目的系统。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0245"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1995-09-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:59.490","remediation":"升级到受支持的现代 Linux 发行版（如 RHEL 9、Ubuntu 22.04+），该漏洞仅在早期 NIS+ 配置中存在，现代版本已修复。检查并移除 /etc/passwd、/etc/shadow、/etc/group 中的单独 \"+\" 通配符条目，将其替换为特定用户或组的显式映射。建议迁移至 LDAP 或 Kerberos 替代 NIS+ 身份验证体系，并在 /etc/hosts.allow 中限制 NIS 相关服务访问来源。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0245"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0430.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0429","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0429.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0244","title":"Livingston RADIUS 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Livingston RADIUS 实现存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，未经认证的远程攻击者可通过向 RADIUS 认证服务发送特制数据包触发缓冲区溢出，导致以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响多个 Livingston 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。建议升级至最新版本或部署访问控制列表限制 RADIUS 服务访问。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0244"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-12-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:59.367","remediation":"立即升级 Livingston RADIUS 至 2.0 及以上版本，该版本修复了 RADIUS 代码中的栈缓冲区溢出漏洞。对于无法升级的旧系统，应在边界防火墙上限制对 RADIUS UDP 端口 1812/1645 的访问来源，仅允许受信任的 NAS 设备 IP 接入。建议迁移至当前仍受支持的 RADIUS 实现（如 FreeRADIUS 3.x），并在运行 RADIUS 服务的主机上启用栈缓冲区溢出保护机制（如 ASLR、NX）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0244","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0244.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0244.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0244","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0244.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0244.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0244.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0244.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--4912a395-3fc6-4764-84b7-7d315af3698f.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0429.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0428","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0428.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0243","title":"Linux cfingerd 远程权限提升漏洞","description":"Linux cfingerd（可配置的 Finger 服务守护进程）存在远程权限提升漏洞，未经身份认证的攻击者可向目标系统发送特制的 Finger 请求触发该漏洞，成功利用后可获取目标系统 root 最高权限，完全控制受影响服务器。该漏洞影响多个 Linux 发行版中运行的 cfingerd 服务，攻击者无需任何认证即可远程发起攻击，危害严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0243"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:59.250","remediation":"立即停止并卸载 cfingerd 服务（`systemctl stop cfingerd && apt-get remove cfingerd` 或 `yum remove cfingerd`）。cfingerd 已在 2000 年代初停止维护，不存在补丁修复。建议在 iptables 或防火墙中封禁 TCP 端口 79，同时禁用 finger 协议。改用现代认证机制（如 LDAP/SSSD）替代 finger 服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.geocrawler.com/archives/3/92/1996/9/0/2217716/","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0243.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0243","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0243.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0243.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0243.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-q27j-g75f-h573/GHSA-q27j-g75f-h573.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/cfinger_format_bug.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x81000/80889/info.html","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/97009c469920f4d8991128f84d19644c3badca15/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-02xx/CVE-1999-0243.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0428.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0427","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0427.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0242","title":"Slackware Linux POP3 邮件文件未授权访问漏洞","description":"部分 Linux 系统（如 Slackware）的 POP3 邮件服务存在认证绕过漏洞，当系统启用影子密码（shadow passwords）时，POP3 守护进程未能正确验证用户凭证，远程攻击者无需有效账号即可通过 POP3 协议访问目标系统上的邮件文件，导致敏感信息泄露。攻击复杂度低，危害较大。受影响系统包括使用 shadow passwords 机制的早期 Linux 发行版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0242"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1995-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:59.133","remediation":"升级 Slackware Linux 的 POP3 守护进程 (如 popper) 到已修复版本，或禁用 POP3 服务改用 IMAP+SSL。确保 /etc/shadow 文件权限为 400 且仅 root 可读，避免使用未加密的 POP3 协议传输密码。如系统已不再维护，建议迁移至受支持的 Linux 发行版。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0242","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0242.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0242.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0242","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0242.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0242.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0242.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0242.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x81000/80898/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154600_154700.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0427.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0426","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0426.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0241","title":"X.Org X Window System 认证令牌可猜测远程代码执行漏洞","description":"X Window System 的 MIT-MAGIC-COOKIE-1 认证机制存在安全缺陷，系统生成的身份认证令牌（magic cookie）使用弱随机数算法，可被远程攻击者通过暴力破解或推测方式获取有效令牌。攻击者成功绕过 X 服务器访问控制后，可通过 xterm 等 X 客户端在目标系统上以当前用户权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响大量运行 X11 协议的操作系统，CVSS v2 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0241"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1995-11-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:59.007","remediation":"升级 XFree86 至 3.3.3 及以上版本，或启用 xdm 的 XDMCP 禁用选项；使用 ssh -X 隧道转发 X11 连接以绕过直接网络暴露；在 hosts.allow 中限制仅允许可信来源的 X11 连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0241","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0241.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0241.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0241.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0241","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0241.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/97009c469920f4d8991128f84d19644c3badca15/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-02xx/CVE-1999-0241.json","https://github.com/justakazh/CVE_Database/blob/06bd07f32c89b43f30d59ff450dfbb661e471cbe/1999/CVE-1999-0241.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/14b23583f5abe84d534fce992127ea0c118b7a95/1999/CVE-1999-0241.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0241.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-nvd/blob/e75163879b5629a697822216993d714626893061/api/1999/CVE-1999-0241.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0426.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0425","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0425.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0240","title":"防火墙或过滤器 IP分片SYN数据包 安全策略绕过漏洞","description":"部分防火墙或网络过滤器在处理分片 SYN 数据包时存在策略绕过漏洞，攻击者可通过向目标网络发送设置了 IP 保留位的特制分片 SYN 数据包，绕过防火墙或过滤器的访问控制规则，未经授权访问受保护的内部网络资源。该漏洞影响多种品牌和型号的防火墙产品，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。厂商通过更新防火墙的分片重组和标志位检查逻辑修复此问题。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0240"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:58.897","remediation":"对防火墙启用状态检测（Stateful Inspection）功能，确保所有IP分片报文在重组完成后再进行规则匹配，禁止直接放行分片SYN包。同时在防火墙上配置策略丢弃IP头部保留位非零的数据包，并禁用非必要接口的IP路由转发功能作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0240","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0240.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0240","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0240.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0240.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0240.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9w2q-p353-cvp5/GHSA-9w2q-p353-cvp5.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0240.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0425.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0424","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0424.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0239","title":"Netscape FastTrack Server 目录列表信息泄露漏洞","description":"tags.<value>Netscape FastTrack Server 3.0.1 存在目录列表漏洞，由于服务器对 HTTP 方法的大小写处理不当，攻击者使用小写的 \"get\" 命令替代标准的大写 \"GET\" 发送请求时，服务器会返回根目录及子目录的文件列表，导致敏感信息泄露。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可利用此漏洞遍历服务器文件系统，获取配置文件、源代码等敏感信息。该漏洞影响 Netscape FastTrack Server 3.0.1 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0239"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:58.770","remediation":"Netscape FastTrack Server 3.0.1 已停止维护超过二十年，官方不再提供安全补丁。建议立即迁移至仍受支持的 Web 服务器（如 Apache HTTP Server、Nginx 或 Microsoft IIS）。若短期内无法迁移，可在反向代理或 WAF 层面配置规则拦截小写 HTTP 方法（将小写 get 请求转换为 400/403 响应）作为临时缓解措施，同时严格限制可访问该服务器的源 IP 范围。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/122","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1731","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19363","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0239.json","https://github.com/kenhuangus/llm-wiki/blob/d2bd485921f6c7b6071afbb389f44ab8e4e83c69/wiki/security/cve/cve-1999-0239.md","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0239","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0239.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0239.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vcjq-7hcj-xh74/GHSA-vcjq-7hcj-xh74.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/netscape_fasttrack.nasl","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_100_200.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0424.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0424.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0424.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0423","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0423.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0238","title":"PHP PHP/fi 2.0 目录遍历漏洞","description":"PHP/FI 2.0 的 php.cgi 脚本存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的 HTTP 请求，利用路径遍历技术读取服务器上的任意文件，包括敏感配置文件、密码文件等。该漏洞影响 PHP/FI 2.0 版本，攻击者无需认证即可利用，危害较大。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0238"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-08-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:58.650","remediation":"立即移除或禁用 PHP/fi 2.0 中的 php.cgi 脚本，升级至 PHP 3.0 或更高版本（PHP 3.0 起已重写架构并修复此目录遍历问题）。如无法升级，在 Web 服务器配置中限制 php.cgi 仅访问指定目录，或通过 .htaccess / httpd.conf 禁止直接访问该脚本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0238","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20567","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0238.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0238","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0238.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0238.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-r5ff-p26w-7pfj/GHSA-r5ff-p26w-7pfj.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/invicti/vulnerabilities/db/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0238.yaml","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0238.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x3000/2250/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0423.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0423.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0423.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0421","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0421.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0236","title":"NCSA HTTPd / Apache httpd ScriptAlias 源代码泄露漏洞","description":"NCSA 1.3/1.4.x/1.5 及 Apache HTTPd 0.8.11/0.8.14 的 ScriptAlias 目录配置存在源码泄露漏洞。攻击者可通过直接访问 ScriptAlias 指定目录下的 CGI 程序文件，绕过服务器对脚本的正常执行处理，从而以明文方式读取 CGI 程序的源代码，导致数据库连接凭证、业务逻辑及内部算法等敏感信息暴露。远程攻击者无需任何身份认证即可利用此漏洞，危害严重。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0236"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:58.393","remediation":"立即升级至 Apache HTTPD 2.4.x 或更新版本（NCSA httpd 已停止维护超过 20 年），该漏洞已在 Apache 1.x 后续版本修复。确保 ScriptAlias 目录配置中不包含源文件读取权限，移除不必要的目录映射并限制 CGI 目录的访问控制。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0236","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20595","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-0236.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0236.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0236","https://github.com/kenhuangus/llm-wiki/blob/d2bd485921f6c7b6071afbb389f44ab8e4e83c69/wiki/security/cve/cve-1999-0236.md","https://github.com/Indie365/cbl-mariner/blob/80d864c0a617439675510c037c8a4589aa596fbb/SPECS/httpd/CVE-1999-0236.nopatch","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0236.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-xgp2-4cpq-g2m7/GHSA-xgp2-4cpq-g2m7.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/invicti/vulnerabilities/db/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0